Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.52,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.99,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.99,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It really is Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:17.36,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.00,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,High school girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:23.75,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.75,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Within 100 kg. You're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:31.13,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I ate so much while cutting down \Non my sweets, but it didn't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:33.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You should think about that, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:36.89,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really what we're taking there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.89,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go in the snow cat, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:42.49,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan, you look like \Nyou could die right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:43.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.14,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:59.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a big boat, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:07.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.16,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.46,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,At least look first.
