Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.37,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lie down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.17,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.27,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.93,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:26.12,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,December is summer here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.63,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,so on warm days, it might not even \Nget below freezing during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.23,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my hand's totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.44,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:45.54,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a quick tour before the \Nstuff arrives and things get crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.96,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Syowa Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:51.76,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That thing that looks like a stack \Nof cubes is the control building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:55.13,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,If this were a house, it would be like \Nthe living room where everyone hangs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.13,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's the generator building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.13,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the residence \Nbuilding and the warehouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.94,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Lakeside Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Lakeside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.64,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's what we call the lodging \Nhouse for the summer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:09.78,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, the members who aren't staying \Nfor the winter would live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:13.39,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,But because there hasn't been maintenance \Nat the other building for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.11,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,and seeing as you're girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.86,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You get your own rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.32,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We get to use all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.75,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,The air is very dry, so be \Nprepared for lots of static.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.87,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,But the floors are heated, \Nand if you open the blinds...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:38.29,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I don't have to worry about the \Nthings Kimari-san rambles in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really talk that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.85,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.17,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,And you do it with your eyes open...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.55,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.20,Flashback,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.76,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The jar genie won't come out of the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.08,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,He probably won't go through the ticket gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.09,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.22,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's the jar genie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:58.65,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.51,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's move on to \Nthe control building...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.12,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Or that was my plan, but I bet the \Nstuff is about to start arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.59,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the heliport.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.54,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.04,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to replace this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:17.33,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.59,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Time for some cleaning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:36.87,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's take a break \Nuntil the next one arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.65,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:38.57,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:40.43,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I worked part-time at a moving company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:43.49,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then rest for ten minutes and then \Nhelp me with the loading over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.87,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I got an email...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.97,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It might have arrived when \Nwe were in the base earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.12,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,We get a cell phone signal \Nnear the control building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.87,sign_8419_76_Shiraishi_Tamiko,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi Tamiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:54.77,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so we can use our smartphones, \Neven in Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Penguins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:05:59.92,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu! The camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.29,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.99,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay within five meters, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.56,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.72,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pen...guin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:09.97,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm filming! Yuzu, grab \Nthe mike and do a report!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.31,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hinata-chan, emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:13.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:15.98,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming toward us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.48,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming... coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.87,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! Stay within five meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.60,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Never a dull moment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.30,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.50,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.86,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to drop \Ndirty snow in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.83,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They said it would get \Nfiltered, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take that off. You'll get sunburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.91,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But it's hard to breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:15.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just been one \Njob after another, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:19.42,Main,shina,0000,0000,0000,,No one's been here for three years, \Nso we'll probably be this busy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.47,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:21.09,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping busy is the best way \Nto speed the clock's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.44,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Another made-up saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.06,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that one up when I was \Nworking at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I think I prefer to keep busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:37.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:38.92,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.73,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I think I like keeping busy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:47.90,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well... we've been traveling \Ntogether for so long, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:48.99,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We have!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:53.12,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about a lot of things \Nand had fun together, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.62,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:56.91,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.91,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I had an audition before we set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.35,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a morning drama. I'll be playing \Nthe best friend of the protagonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,No way! And you got the part?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,sign_11628_121_Shiraishi_Tamiko,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi Tamiko\N{\c&H7E8382&}It's decided! Well done!\N{\c&H7E8382&}You passed the audition for the morning drama! \NCongratulations! Great job!\NLove, Mom\NSent from myPhone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.17,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.68,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But when the drama starts shooting, \NI'll have a lot less time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.22,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to hang out \Ntogether like this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.92,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even without the drama, \Nwe'd be living separately again anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.28,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:24.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We're all best friends already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.84,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Best friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.32,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Are we best friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:34.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:38.28,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't you say before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.74,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,that you'd only just met?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at the time, that was the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.41,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,So when did you decide you were best friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:51.63,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Did it happen while I was in Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.79,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.90,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It did, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:56.64,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.14,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you, without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.39,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Without ever telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:13.28,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there's nothing we've \Ndone without telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.78,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't trust anyone, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.13,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there is one \Nthing we haven't told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:27.35,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But we are still friends. All of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.32,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:33.35,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. No time in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.80,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's what being friends is, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:41.06,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But you never told me you \Nwanted to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.83,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have another productive day tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.28,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,When did we become friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:59.89,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You think she was waiting this whole time \Nfor someone to say, "Let's be friends"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.65,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We could just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:03.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:06.39,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,"You're obviously just saying \Nthat because I made you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.08,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.03,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How's Kimari doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:12.05,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. She said she could handle it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:17.28,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But she's so bold about some things \Nand so timid about others...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.85,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Helmets good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.04,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Helmets good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.90,sign_15094_167_Lunch_Menu__Chri,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch Menu!\N{\c&H907E61&}Christmas Antarctica Special
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.04,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Chin straps good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.32,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Chin straps good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.41,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Health good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.69,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Health good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.71,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Feet good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.91,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Feet good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.62,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have another productive day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.74,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.67,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.78,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:45.11,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They said we'd get to work indoors...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But it's colder in here than it is outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.12,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,My nose is getting red!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.00,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They're conserving energy, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.67,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We need to keep the indoor work short.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.80,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This is all of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.45,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.49,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Next, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,A chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.15,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:04.01,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to find somewhere \Nwarm to defrost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.12,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I had a few I set defrosting yesterday, \Nbut it doesn't look like it'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.35,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.31,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.78,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:16.01,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,And you two can stay here and help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:16.90,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.90,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be the best place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.66,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That seems unspeakably dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.41,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What about here, in the sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It never sets here, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.58,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They're both birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.41,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that matters to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.90,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,There are penguins here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.28,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Do they eat chicken, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.46,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.70,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,There, that should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.34,sign_16768_205_Defrosting,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Defrosting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.34,sign_16768_206_Touch_and_you_di,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Touch and\Nyou die
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But how are things going \Nwith the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:49.48,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, today's pick-me-up is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.63,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.90,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.96,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Is Christmas that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.40,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the most important \Nparts of life on the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.38,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.40,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Food and events.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.92,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be living a spartan life in a \Nlimited space for a long time, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:09.00,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.75,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your pick-me-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.25,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.47,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.51,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.44,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.51,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:28.01,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like a birthday, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.06,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.27,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:36.43,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody has a birthday, yet there are \Npeople whose birthdays get celebrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.27,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,and people whose birthdays don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.43,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your song?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.63,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get the \Nexternal shots in advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.89,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:07.51,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Since they said we might not be able \Nto go outside if the wind picks up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.05,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,About that thing I mentioned before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.71,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to do the drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.80,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I gave it a lot of thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.78,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,and apparently some people here \Nmay be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.46,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:26.41,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:31.27,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,So, could I ask a favor of you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Could you fill this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.08,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:43.09,sign_19567_247_Friendship_Contr,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship Contract
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.10,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,This way, even after our adventure is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:43.09,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,and we're not around each other \Nas often, I know we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.10,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.66,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,This won't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.15,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I've been all alone before, so I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.08,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You can't know, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.71,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave a scrap behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.79,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't clean your plate, \Nyou'll be denied bathroom privileges!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.26,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,Still partially frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.20,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, partially frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:41.02,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,It says "partially frozen\Nrice bowl" on the menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.52,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,That's one way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan, want seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:48.79,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:51.99,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:59.00,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... after dinner, I was \Nhoping to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.00,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have something \NI have to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.51,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.28,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.35,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I know what to say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:13.85,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Then, should we lay off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.18,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.53,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:21.73,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. She's not mad, or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.41,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But Kimari-san cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.23,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I think she felt hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.54,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's all on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ditch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.37,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Have I done something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:37.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I wouldn't say "strange."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:41.47,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in your position, \NI'd probably feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:42.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.38,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:48.41,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship isn't about lots of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.83,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.10,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.32,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:58.85,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's about... feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.25,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.34,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, let's say you \Ntell Kimari you like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:08.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari doesn't believe you, so she wants \Nyou to write it down on a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.89,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You'd hate that, right? \NYou'd feel like she didn't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:11.95,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.23,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:18.04,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably why she was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.53,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, Kimari already sees you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.93,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But what makes us friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.17,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,How do you become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.47,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:33.97,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably no real way to define it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.47,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like a parental \Nor spousal relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.11,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's more vague than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No one's to blame if it fades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.19,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's the case for me, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.67,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what lets it feel unrestrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's what lets us be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.36,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.50,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.50,sign_24552_313_4__Antarctic_Mag,gin,0000,0000,0000,,4. Antarctic Magic Show\N5. Christmas Stories {\c&H7B5BC8&}Two {\c&H424444&}High School Girls\N6. Golden Oldies Old Man Choir\N7. Wrap! Wrap! Burp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Are there good children here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.17,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Are there good children here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.51,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why even bother with the performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.87,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you make us do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.27,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari told us to, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.62,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.24,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.57,sign_11628_121_Shiraishi_Tamiko,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!\NI'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.57,sign_25208_324_I_m_sorry,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.57,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.08,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,M-Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.23,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:47.21,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.54,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.24,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.84,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Could we talk for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.84,sign_11628_121_Shiraishi_Tamiko,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!\NI'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.84,sign_25208_324_I_m_sorry,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:59.23,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to settle down when \Nit stays dusk like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.49,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the day never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.29,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're angry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.85,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't write back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Because you didn't have \Nanything to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.09,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:18.74,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Megu-chan has been my best \Nfriend since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:24.14,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Right before I headed out, she said \Nshe wanted to break things off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.41,sign_26440_342_Singapore___,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Arrived in Singapore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.44,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I still think of her as a friend, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.49,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't respond often, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.25,sign_26544_343_Australia___,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1100,1)}Arrived in Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.25,sign_26553_344_I_see_,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1)}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:30.80,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow, I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.70,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm watching the screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:36.10,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,and it pops up with the \Nlittle "message read" sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.26,sign_26553_344_I_see_ - Copy,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Message Read
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She writes something back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes right away, \Nsometimes after a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.11,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes half a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:47.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Each time I see it, I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:50.96,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah, I bet she's at school right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.13,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"I bet she's in bed."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"I bet she's not sure whether \Nor not she should respond."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.78,sign_27256_358_Send,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Send
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.13,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just how she's feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:03.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's what friends are for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:13.28,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally vague, I know, \Nbut that's what it is for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.14,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I guess that \Ndoesn't solve anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.79,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.85,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.06,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan, it's was your \Nbirthday before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:36.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But we spent so long being \Nseasick at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.03,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:41.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari suggested that we should \Ncelebrate it in Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.49,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We had Yumiko-san set the ingredients aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:47.29,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just fill in the parts we \Nmessed up with your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.29,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:54.99,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:55.80,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, blow them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.05,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like the first \Ntime we met you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.84,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.03,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Blow them out before they melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:10.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.81,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.74,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.93,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,it's the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.07,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,friends have celebrated my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.18,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Yuzuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:33.96,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.17,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:44.22,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up my first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.61,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a pick-me-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:05.91,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.45,sign_30459_394_Sorry,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1347)}Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.87,sign_11628_121_Shiraishi_Tamiko,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!\NI'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.87,sign_25208_324_I_m_sorry,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.12,sign_30523_395_Good_morn,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1191,264)}Good morn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.63,sign_30594_396_Thank_you,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2277,270)}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:25.39,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But when the question gets put to \Nyou, it's hard to express it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.33,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, what friends are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:27.93,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:31.67,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, after you burn it, \Nthere's so little left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:36.04,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But they say when they take back a whole \Nyear's worth of garbage it'll be like a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:41.15,sign_31148_402_Sorry_Thanks,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sorry\NThanks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.11,sign_31148_402_Sorry_Thanks,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:45.99,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:49.53,sign_31148_402_Sorry_Thanks,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:49.89,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I think friendship is this one little word!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.87,sign_31148_402_Sorry_Thanks,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:53.03,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that quote?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:55.43,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But it's better than your quotes, Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:04.01,sign_31148_402_Sorry_Thanks,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:04.01,sign_31576_412_Right,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.01,sign_31148_402_Sorry_Thanks - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,Right
